Key Match Events: Danley Jean Jacques equalized in the 50th minute
Frantzdy Pierrot gave Haiti the lead with a goal in the 59th minute
Don Deedson Louicius widened the gap for Haiti by scoring a goal in the 76th minute
Duckens Nazon crowned the victory by scoring the last goal in the 83rd minute
Pre-Game Insights: French coach Sébastien Migné revealed the composition of his team. Among the notable choices, we note the starting position of young midfielder Belmar Joseph Jr.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the opening match in League B of the Nations League (CNL) of the Confederation of North, Central American and Caribbean Countries (CONCACAF)
Others: The upcoming match schedule includes Haiti vs Sint-Maarten on September 9, 2024, at 5:00 p.m.
